  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience Royal Landscaping with a Touch of Madness!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Queen's Garden: French Splendor</i> takes you on a hilarious journey through the world of high-society gardening. Step into the shoes of a royal landscape architect and prove that you have the \"green thumb\" required to satisfy the crown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Dynamic Duo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won’t be gardening alone! <strong>Meet our resident experts</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/042227ce553385d6fa56702405eafa51.avif?t=1767218151\" width=875 height=748 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Marigold:</strong> A perfectionist head gardener who treats every wilted leaf like a personal insult and won't rest until every hedge is symmetrical. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Florian:</strong> The charming assistant whose idea of \"hard work\" is complimenting the weeds on their tenacity and taking long naps in the topiary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through match-3 puzzles that'll grow on you faster than kudzu, you'll transform a garden that looks like it was hit by a tornado riding a lawnmower into a paradise that would make Versailles jealous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Game Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >110 levels of matching madness (because 109 was just not enough)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-ups that make your average garden gnome look boring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate a French garden so fancy, even snails wear berets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay so addictive, you'll forget what the sun looks like (ironic for a gardening game)</p></li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Experience Royal Landscaping with a Touch of Madness!</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Queen's Garden: French Splendor</i> takes you on a hilarious journey through the world of high-society gardening. Step into the shoes of a royal landscape architect and prove that you have the \"green thumb\" required to satisfy the crown.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/9ac5e3c77ec9d0d2eba3d3534d04a6c0.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Dynamic Duo</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You won’t be gardening alone! <strong>Meet our resident experts</strong>:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/042227ce553385d6fa56702405eafa51.avif?t=1767218151\" width=875 height=748 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Marigold:</strong> A perfectionist head gardener who treats every wilted leaf like a personal insult and won't rest until every hedge is symmetrical. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Florian:</strong> The charming assistant whose idea of \"hard work\" is complimenting the weeds on their tenacity and taking long naps in the topiary.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/d120b784d67caa18f98423b78a1c5e60.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Through match-3 puzzles that'll grow on you faster than kudzu, you'll transform a garden that looks like it was hit by a tornado riding a lawnmower into a paradise that would make Versailles jealous.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/8619ba463cf947edd74c9e9f512d8840.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.poster.avif?t=1767218151\" width=510 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.webm?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3049410/extras/ce8696f1086018923886e8271e5b7e10.mp4?t=1767218151\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Key Game Features</strong> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >110 levels of matching madness (because 109 was just not enough)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Power-ups that make your average garden gnome look boring</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Decorate a French garden so fancy, even snails wear berets</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gameplay so addictive, you'll forget what the sun looks like (ironic for a gardening game)</p></li></ul>",
